00:04:30.680 --> 00:04:33.680
Tu es ma seule famille dans ce monde.

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:34.960
Ne pars pas.

00:04:35.240 --> 00:04:37.480
Ne me quitte pas, Père.

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:46.400
Va vite.

00:04:49.760 --> 00:04:50.520
Aller!

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:54.960
Père!

00:04:57.960 --> 00:04:58.760
Allez-y maintenant !

00:05:03.080 --> 00:05:03.960
